item.title: 5.12.12 for macOS
item.description: Important FINAL VERSION, NO MORE UPDATES EVEN IF REQUESTED, BUILD ENVIRONMENT HAS BEEN DESTRUCTED Note SQLite(distributed with Qt) are built in the backage and have -plugin-sql-sqlite Note All builds have -no-openssl -securetransport. It means that we are using Secure Transport library of macOS to provide SSL connections. Note All builds have -no-icu because I think the ICU library is too big and, in most of the conditions, useless for common users.

item.title: 5.12.12 for WebAssembly
item.description: Important FINAL VERSION, NO MORE UPDATES EVEN IF REQUESTED, BUILD ENVIRONMENT HAS BEEN DESTRUCTED Note SQLite(distributed with Qt) are built in the backage and have -plugin-sql-sqlite Note All builds have -no-icu because I think the ICU library is too big and, in most of the conditions, useless for common users. Note All builds are using emscripten SDK 1.38.16 as recommended in Qt Wiki. Note Qt for WebAssembly can’t be built to shared libs.
